Name: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' across all cases
Metric: Number of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' activities

Name: Percentage of variants where 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' is immediately followed by 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 3 days'
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 3 days'

Name: Frequency of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' occurring before 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: Number of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' activities for cases where activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' occurs

Name: Percentage of cases containing 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' that eventually lead to 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Ratio of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' to 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' in the entire log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' out of all 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' occurrences that are not followed by any reviewer agreement (i.e., no 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' later in the same case)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' out of all cases where 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' does not happen

Name: Frequency of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' in variants that end with a rejection decision ('SW-EIC Reject', 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit')
Metric: Number of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Reject' occurs

Name: Percentage of cases where 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' appears more than once
Metric: the average of the function base > 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week'

Name: Frequency of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' compared to other deadline-related notifications such as 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 3 days' and 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due'
Metric: Number of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 3 days' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' that occur after 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' but before any 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' out of all 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Ratio of cases containing 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' that result in eventual acceptance ('RW-EIC Accept' or 'SW-EIC Accept') versus those resulting in rejection
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Frequency of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' in long-running cases (performance > median variant duration) versus short-running cases
Metric: Number of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' activities

Name: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' that are followed within 7 days by 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Frequency of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' appearing in variants that include at least one 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'
Metric: Number of 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' activities for cases where activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1' occurs
